Style meets engineering in the Reebok Twistform Blaze 3.0 Running Shoes for men. The Twistform technique streamlines the look, while transitional waves on the sole propel your efforts past expectations, resulting in a superior training expieriance. 3DFuseFrame upper for lightweight support
Low-cut design for freedom of motion at the ankles
Foam compound provides a soft feel underfoot
Enhanced transition waves propel you forward
Strategically placed outsole rubber for increased traction
Midsole paint line focuses on heel support
Outsole geometry for flexibility

The Twistform technique streamlines the look, while transitional waves on the sole propel your efforts past expectations, resulting in a superior training expieriance. Go all day with comfort from the cushioned foam midsole.
3DFuseFrame upper for lightweight support
Low-cut design for freedom of motion at the ankles
Foam compound provides a soft feel underfoot
Enhanced transition waves propel you forward
Strategically placed outsole rubber for increased traction
Midsole paint line focuses on heel support
Outsole geometry for flexibility
Targeted Group: Men
Occasion: Twistform Blaze 3.0 Running Shoe
Style: Sneakers
Color: Grey
Size EU: 43
